# Coming Soon mode disabled on 2026-04-23. All routes publicly accessible.
# Cloudflare Pages handles clean-URL .html routing automatically — no rewrites needed here.

# Genki QR box landing (2026-05-15) — /box/[CODE] is handled by the Pages
# Function at functions/box/[[code]].js, which serves box-landing.html for
# every path under /box/ while keeping the original URL (so the page JS can
# read the CODE from location.pathname).
#
# Only /box (no trailing path) needs a rule — the Function doesn't catch it
# (Pages catch-alls require at least one segment). Send /box to /box-landing
# so a code-less visit still lands on the page.
/box   /box-landing   301
